column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/d90491a766e7ab5e9cc0a6207fe8ad88a803dfb1 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
Merged this because it is trivial, but please next time use a clearer commit message title instead of 'Update test_main.cpp'.\n
